data.meta_description: Mark David Protosevich (born August 24, 1961) is an American screenwriter. He wrote the screenplays for the films Poseidon and I Am Legend. Protosevich was born in Chicago, Illinois and is an alumnus of Columbia College Chicago. Protosevich also wrote the script for the unproduced Batman Unchained.
